historyItem.sql: select cluster_name acode, cluster_name adescription from safe_cluster_info where lower(cluster_type) in ('u', 'c') and lower(cluster_name) like lower('%' || :q || '%') and ( lower(cluster_public ) = 'y' or lower(cluster_created_by) = lower(:Uidtoken) ) and ( lower(nvl(cluster_user_role, lower(:userRoleName))) like lower(:userRoleName) or cluster_user_role is null )
